metadata.name: Digital Evil Eye Encryption
metadata.description: The luxurious, yet indisputably modern evil eye encryption necklace or bracelet that you'll never want to take off. It is handcrafted with special care and designed with a gorgeous glare. The deep blue slice diamond comes alive and spreads good luck and protection. This Evil Eye Encryption piece keeps you secure from unauthorized access to your spirit in both the digital and physical worlds. Redeemable as a necklace or bracelet, both are customizable in size and adjustable to any length up to 18cm. Materials: 18K Rose and White Gold Plated on Silver, Total Weight 3.76 g. Blue Slice Diamonds, Round Diamonds, Total weight 0.28 (cts). All sizes adjustable up to 18cm. Include note: all sizes adjustable up to 18cm. Note: The Digital Evil Eye Encryption exists only in the digital world.

attributes.value: Blue Slice Diamonds, Round Diamonds, Total Diamond Weight 0.28 cts, 18K Rose and White Gold Plated on Silver
